<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/971556-hello-folks-as-i-read-chapter-36-of-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Hello folks,<br />As I read chapter 36 of the book, it seemed clear to me that this book happens in the same 'universe' than "Fountains of paradise". Early in the book it is mentioned how the Gibraltar bridge was totally destroyed. And in this chapter he mentions space elevators and that super resistant material the elevator cables were made of.<br />Did anybody else notice this? What do you guys think about it? :) <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
